Package org.goplanit.utils.zoning

Interface Zone

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<IdAble>, ExternalIdAble, IdAble, ManagedId
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    OdZone, TransferZone
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OdZoneImpl, TransferZoneImpl, ZoneImpl
    public interface Zone
extends ExternalIdAble, ManagedId
    Zone represent a geographical area with a centroid which in turn represent the single point of departure of all traffic in the zone
    Author:
    markr
